12be0b49b8ee30530588abad6d81f937b24c4f8c","tid":2371124,"uid":115728,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"因為你中左弓形蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"人要是真想通過寵物來感染「弓形蟲」其實並不是一件簡單的事情，要按照如下步驟嚴格執行，你才有可能中招。要想從寵物身上成功感染「弓形蟲」，你必須做到以下5點才行：<br />\n<br />\n&radic; 得養貓，養狗沒用<br />\n<br />\n&radic; 得先餵貓吃生肉，吃貓糧不行，必須先確保貓感染弓形蟲<br />\n<br />\n&radic; 然後再吃貓屎，喝貓尿沒用，必須吃貓屎<br />\n<br />\n&radic; 貓屎不要趁熱吃，必須吃超過24小時的隔夜貓屎（貓糞便中的弓形蟲卵，則需要在外界發育2天以上才會變得有傳染性）<br />\n<br />\n&radic; 以上4點都做到了也未必成功，因為貓一輩子只排一次弓形蟲卵，所以必須頓頓不漏的吃屎，堅持下去才有可能成功感染弓形蟲！"},{"pid":"9b614e307deacc8d5195c498fd1e634f36056360","tid":2371124,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7553cb50dda67c374d79b3b2e2e56cf9186c0a8b","tid":2371124,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f270782a82359beaf15df73e9e99deed09b6b6","tid":2371124,"uid":2786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12be0b49b8ee30530588abad6d81f937b24c4f8c","tid":2371124,"uid":115728,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:26:27.000Z","msg":"因為你中左弓形蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 養貓前都唔覺貓有味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T15:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />甜味"},{"pid":"6cf1f98750381882db342291d59a23dd8a70f2a8","tid":2371124,"uid":63163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b614e307deacc8d5195c498fd1e634f36056360","tid":2371124,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7553cb50dda67c374d79b3b2e2e56cf9186c0a8b","tid":2371124,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47f270782a82359beaf15df7